name: APOD
0:
”Alexa, open astro picture”
”Alexa, ask astro picture for today's picture”
”Alexa, ask astro picture to show me today's picture”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: astro picture
des:
A simple skill to show the Astronomy Picture of the Day on your Alexa enabled device with a display along with its title.

Your device MUST have a display to use this skill, e.g. Echo Show or Spot. This skill is currently unsupported for devices without a display.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
